<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="en">
<head>
    <meta charset="UTF-8">
    <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0">
    <title>Document Expiry Notice</title>
    <style>
        body {
            font-family: 'Inter', -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, 'Segoe UI', Roboto, sans-serif;
            line-height: 1.6;
            color: #0A0A0A;
            background-color: #FFFFFF;
            margin: 0;
            padding: 0;
        }
        .container {
            max-width: 600px;
            margin: 0 auto;
            padding: 20px;
        }
        .header {
            text-align: center;
            padding: 40px 0;
            border-bottom: 1px solid #E5E5E5;
        }
        .logo {
            font-size: 24px;
            font-weight: 600;
            color: #171717;
        }
        .content {
            padding: 40px 0;
        }
        .page-title {
            font-size: 24px;
            font-weight: 600;
            color: #171717;
            margin-bottom: 20px;
        }
        .urgency-critical {
            background-color: #FEF2F2;
            border: 1px solid #FECACA;
            border-left: 4px solid #EF4444;
            padding: 16px;
            border-radius: 6px;
            margin: 20px 0;
            color: #7F1D1D;
        }
        .urgency-warning {
            background-color: #FEF3C7;
            border: 1px solid #FDE68A;
            border-left: 4px solid #F59E0B;
            padding: 16px;
            border-radius: 6px;
            margin: 20px 0;
            color: #92400E;
        }
        .urgency-notice {
            background-color: #F5F5F5;
            border: 1px solid #E5E5E5;
            border-left: 4px solid #171717;
            padding: 16px;
            border-radius: 6px;
            margin: 20px 0;
            color: #525252;
        }
        .document-info {
            background-color: #F5F5F5;
            padding: 20px;
            border-radius: 8px;
            margin: 20px 0;
        }
        .info-row {
            display: flex;
            justify-content: space-between;
            margin-bottom: 10px;
            padding-bottom: 10px;
            border-bottom: 1px solid #E5E5E5;
        }
        .info-row:last-child {
            margin-bottom: 0;
            padding-bottom: 0;
            border-bottom: none;
        }
        .info-label {
            font-weight: 500;
            color: #737373;
        }
        .info-value {
            font-weight: 600;
            color: #171717;
        }
        .expiry-highlight {
            color: #EF4444;
        }
        .action-required {
            background-color: #F5F5F5;
            padding: 16px 20px;
            border-radius: 8px;
            margin: 20px 0;
            font-size: 14px;
        }
        .action-required h3 {
            margin: 0 0 8px 0;
            font-size: 14px;
            color: #171717;
        }
        .action-required p {
            margin: 0;
            color: #525252;
        }
        .footer {
            text-align: center;
            padding: 20px 0;
            border-top: 1px solid #E5E5E5;
            color: #737373;
            font-size: 14px;
        }
    </style>
</head>
<body>
    <div class="container">
        <div class="header">
            <div class="logo">Employee Management System</div>
        </div>

        <div class="content">
            <h1 class="page-title">Document Expiry Notice</h1>

            <p>Dear {{employeeName}},</p>

            <p>This is an important notice regarding a document on your profile that is approaching its expiry date.</p>

            {{#if (lt daysRemaining 8)}}
            <div class="urgency-critical">
                <strong>Urgent:</strong> This document expires in <strong>{{daysRemaining}} {{#if (eq daysRemaining 1)}}day{{else}}days{{/if}}</strong>. Immediate action is required to avoid any disruption to your employment records.
            </div>
            {{else if (lt daysRemaining 31)}}
            <div class="urgency-warning">
                <strong>Action Required:</strong> This document expires in <strong>{{daysRemaining}} days</strong>. Please renew or update it as soon as possible.
            </div>
            {{else}}
            <div class="urgency-notice">
                <strong>Advance Notice:</strong> This document will expire in <strong>{{daysRemaining}} days</strong>. Please plan to renew it before the expiry date.
            </div>
            {{/if}}

            <div class="document-info">
                <div class="info-row">
                    <span class="info-label">Document Name:</span>
                    <span class="info-value">{{documentName}}</span>
                </div>
                <div class="info-row">
                    <span class="info-label">Expiry Date:</span>
                    <span class="info-value expiry-highlight">{{expiryDate}}</span>
                </div>
                <div class="info-row">
                    <span class="info-label">Days Remaining:</span>
                    <span class="info-value expiry-highlight">{{daysRemaining}} {{#if (eq daysRemaining 1)}}day{{else}}days{{/if}}</span>
                </div>
            </div>

            <div class="action-required">
                <h3>Action Required:</h3>
                <p>{{actionRequired}}</p>
            </div>

            <p>Please upload the renewed document through the employee portal or hand it over to the HR department. Failure to renew may affect your compliance status.</p>

            <p>If you have already submitted the renewed document, please disregard this notice. Contact HR if you need any assistance.</p>
        </div>

        <div class="footer">
            <p>This is an automated message from the Employee Management System.</p>
        </div>
    </div>
</body>
</html>
